 2002-17382002-10-08,  ,  NR,  , 
PrecisAppointment of BROCK SMITH of Scarborough, Ontario, selected from a list of nominees submitted by the Province of Ontario, to be a director of the Board of Management of the Canada Customs and Revenue Agency, to hold office during pleasure for a term of two years, in the place of Michael Gourley, who has resigned.
